{"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/anycable/anycable-rails/releases/28087826", "assets_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/anycable/anycable-rails/releases/28087826/assets", "upload_url": "https://uploads.github.com/repos/anycable/anycable-rails/releases/28087826/assets{?name,label}", "html_url": "https://github.com/anycable/anycable-rails/releases/tag/v1.0.0", "id": 28087826, "author": {"login": "palkan", "id": 1516722, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjE1MTY3MjI=", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1516722?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/palkan", "html_url": "https://github.com/palkan", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/palkan/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/palkan/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/palkan/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/palkan/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/palkan/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/palkan/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/palkan/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/palkan/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/palkan/received_events", "type": "User", "site_admin": false}, "node_id": "MDc6UmVsZWFzZTI4MDg3ODI2", "tag_name": "v1.0.0", "target_commitish": "master", "name": "1.0.0", "draft": false, "prerelease": false, "created_at": "2020-06-30T20:49:47Z", "published_at": "2020-06-30T20:56:59Z", "assets": [], "tarball_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/anycable/anycable-rails/tarball/v1.0.0", "zipball_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/anycable/anycable-rails/zipball/v1.0.0", "body": "See the project's [release notes](https://docs.anycable.io/v1/#/release_notes) for more information on all AnyCable libraries.\r\n\r\nPlease, checkout the [upgrade notes](https://docs.anycable.io/v1/#/upgrade-notes/0_6_0_to_1_0_0) to learn how to migrate from 0.6 to 1.0.\r\n\r\n## Features\r\n\r\n- Added interactive `rails g anycable:setup` command for initial AnyCable configuration.\r\n\r\n- Added `request` support to channels.\r\n\r\nNow you can access underlying HTTP request data in channels, too.\r\n\r\n- Added Rack middleware support (incl. out-of-the-box Rails sessions support).\r\n\r\nYou can _enhance_ request object by passing it through a custom middleware chain (e.g., when using Warden for authentication). By default, we include Rails session middleware, which makes `request.session` available in AnyCable without any hacks.\r\n\r\nSee [documentation](https://docs.anycable.io/v1/#/ruby/authentication).\r\n\r\n- Added `state_attr_accessor` to persist channels state.\r\n\r\nSee [documentation](https://docs.anycable.io/v1/#/ruby/channels_state).\r\n\r\n- Added support for `ActionCable.server.remote_connections.where(...).disconnect`.\r\n\r\n- **Added compatibility with Rails 6.1**.\r\n\r\nIncluding `type: :disconnect` messages, `Connection.rescue_from`, `stop_stream_from`.\r\n\r\n## Changes\r\n\r\n- Using `anycable-go` v1.x is required.\r\n\r\n"}
{"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/anycable/anycable-rails/releases/13964271", "assets_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/anycable/anycable-rails/releases/13964271/assets", "upload_url": "https://uploads.github.com/repos/anycable/anycable-rails/releases/13964271/assets{?name,label}", "html_url": "https://github.com/anycable/anycable-rails/releases/tag/v0.6.0", "id": 13964271, "author": {"login": "palkan", "id": 1516722, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjE1MTY3MjI=", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1516722?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/palkan", "html_url": "https://github.com/palkan", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/palkan/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/palkan/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/palkan/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/palkan/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/palkan/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/palkan/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/palkan/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/palkan/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/palkan/received_events", "type": "User", "site_admin": false}, "node_id": "MDc6UmVsZWFzZTEzOTY0Mjcx", "tag_name": "v0.6.0", "target_commitish": "master", "name": "0.6.0 \"Old School Hollywood\" \ud83c\udfa5", "draft": false, "prerelease": false, "created_at": "2018-11-15T07:30:06Z", "published_at": "2018-11-15T07:33:21Z", "assets": [], "tarball_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/anycable/anycable-rails/tarball/v0.6.0", "zipball_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/anycable/anycable-rails/zipball/v0.6.0", "body": "[RubyConf 2018](http://rubyconf.org) special.\r\n\r\n**tl;dr** use `anycable` CLI instead of generator; use `:any_cable` subscription adapter for Action Cable to _activate_ AnyCable.\r\n\r\n**NOTE:** this version has been yanked from RubyGems due to the regression bug. Use 0.6.1.\r\n\r\nThis release requires `anycable` gem >= 0.6.0. See [release notes](https://github.com/anycable/anycable/releases/tag/v0.6.0) for `anycable` 0.6.0.\r\n\r\nSee also [upgrade notes](https://docs.anycable.io/#/upgrade_to_0_6_0?id=rails).\r\n\r\n### Changes\r\n\r\n- No more generators.\r\n\r\nNo need to generate AnyCable runner script since `anycable` gem ships with the [CLI](https://docs.anycable.io/#/anycable_gem).\r\n\r\nScripts generated by the previous version should work (unless have a non-generated code).\r\n\r\n- **[Breaking]** Added `:any_cable` subscription adapter for Action Cable.\r\n\r\nUse `:any_cable` adapter for Action Cable to broadcast data to AnyCable.\r\n\r\nAction Cable monkey-patches are only loaded in the context of AnyCable CLI. ([@palkan][])\r\n\r\nNo need to think about `require` and `group` for `anycable-rails`, just add it to Gemfile.\r\n\r\n### Features\r\n\r\n- Added support for request verification based on ActionCable config (`disable_forgery_protection`, `allow_same_origin_as_host` and `allowed_request_origins`)\r\n\r\n- Add compatibility checks.\r\n\r\nSee [documentation](https://docs.anycable.io/#/compatibility).\r\n\r\n- Add WS server session ID to log tags if present.\r\n\r\nSession ID feature is supported by [`anycable-go`](https://github.com/anycable/anycable-go/releases/tag/v0.6.0) >= 0.6.0.\r\n\r\n### Improvements\r\n\r\n- Tagged logging is supported (was ignored previously).\r\n\r\n- Added Rails executor/reloader support.\r\n\r\nNow code changes are handled by RPC server (in development)."}
{"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/anycable/anycable-rails/releases/8206357", "assets_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/anycable/anycable-rails/releases/8206357/assets", "upload_url": "https://uploads.github.com/repos/anycable/anycable-rails/releases/8206357/assets{?name,label}", "html_url": "https://github.com/anycable/anycable-rails/releases/tag/v0.5.0", "id": 8206357, "author": {"login": "palkan", "id": 1516722, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjE1MTY3MjI=", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1516722?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/palkan", "html_url": "https://github.com/palkan", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/palkan/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/palkan/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/palkan/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/palkan/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/palkan/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/palkan/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/palkan/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/palkan/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/palkan/received_events", "type": "User", "site_admin": false}, "node_id": "MDc6UmVsZWFzZTgyMDYzNTc=", "tag_name": "v0.5.0", "target_commitish": "master", "name": "v0.5.0", "draft": false, "prerelease": false, "created_at": "2017-10-21T11:15:24Z", "published_at": "2017-10-21T11:45:30Z", "assets": [], "tarball_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/anycable/anycable-rails/tarball/v0.5.0", "zipball_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/anycable/anycable-rails/zipball/v0.5.0", "body": "### Features\r\n\r\n- Refactored logging.\r\n\r\nNow we use Rails logger everywhere. That means, for example, that `ANYCABLE_DEBUG=1` won't work anymore, set your `config.log_level` to `:debug` instead.\r\n\r\n- Access logging added (disabled by default).\r\n\r\nYou can enable Action Cable-like access logs:\r\n\r\n```yml\r\n# anycable.yml\r\nproduction:\r\n  access_logs_disabled: false\r\n```\r\n\r\nNow you can find in your logs:\r\n\r\n```\r\nStarted \"/cable\" [Anycable] for  at 2017-10-21 12:32:32 +0300\r\n...\r\nFinished \"/cable\" [Anycable] for  at 2017-10-21 12:32:35 +0300 (Closed)\r\n```\r\n\r\nSee also [release notes](https://github.com/anycable/anycable/releases/tag/v0.5.0) for `anycable` gem."}
